{"tid":818664,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"廢青飲酒谷再次招人啦(2)","createTime":"2018-09-14T09:02:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T05:52:15.000Z","uid":5849,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"3e7733cb8e31f129e81e25c1fc7b2351a9a7f017","tid":818664,"uid":5849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:02:49.000Z","msg":"谷已經開咗差唔多半年啦<br />\n每個星期都會出去一次<br />\n除咗飲酒都會搞下其他活動，打邊爐etc <br />\n係咁當然飲酒多，話明飲酒谷吖ma<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/14/165449_beaf11ffb1bfa8809a550fd15b8a3da3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F14%2F165449_beaf11ffb1bfa8809a550fd15b8a3da3.png&h=591d5cb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n輕輕鬆鬆，On99啱傾就入谷啦<br />\n有控制人數，禁止小圈子<br />\n因為每個會員都可以講野<br />\n男女人數平衡，維持一定人數嘅谷<br />\n啱晒怕羞絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔似其他谷成百幾二百人，都唔知邊個打邊個<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">謝絕狗公同無聊人士<br />\n精神不正常，唔該有啲自知之明<br />\n<br />\n另外諗清楚先好入谷，有啲入咗完全唔講嘢都唔知做咩<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有意者留TG"},{"pid":"d07bfc6ec10007c89c738244fb8f83742a8a87d3","tid":818664,"uid":5849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其他相有太多人費事post"},{"pid":"deb4eb25988283319ce04065fb19d63663d143ff","tid":818664,"uid":5849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:11:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c58fa4a38655584df457727276a33d90037172","tid":818664,"uid":5849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:15:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e73263babb9fb528ed4a50cd5ab8f7185fc7f58f","tid":818664,"uid":5849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:24:28.0